#### Replication Network Failover (optional manual test)

To verify failover works, temporarily disable one interface on a node and
confirm the fallback route takes over:

```bash
# On {{ nodes[0].name }}: disable direct link to {{ nodes[1].name }}
ssh root@{{ nodes[0].mgmt_ip }} ip link set {{ nodes[0].repl_peers[nodes[1].name].iface }} down
# Verify {{ nodes[1].name }}'s corosync address is still reachable (via {{ nodes[2].name }})
ssh root@{{ nodes[0].mgmt_ip }} ping -c 3 {{ nodes[1].repl_ip }}
# Re-enable the link
ssh root@{{ nodes[0].mgmt_ip }} ip link set {{ nodes[0].repl_peers[nodes[1].name].iface }} up
```
{%- endif %}

